"title": "8628: worship, hindrances to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8628",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>True worship goes beyond mere form and can therefore be hindered by a wrong relationship to God or to others.</p>\n<h2>Worship that is merely formal is unacceptable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:13\">ISA 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:31\">EZK 33:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">HOS 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5\">MAT 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:5\">2TI 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Worship is hindered by wrong relationships</h2>\n<h3>To God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:18\">PSA 66:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:7-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:7–15:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6-Mark7:7\">MRK 7:6–7:7</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:5-Ps32:6\">PSA 32:5–32:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:2\">ISA 59:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:7\">ISA 64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:3\">JAS 4:3</a></p>\n<h3>To others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:11-Isa1:17\">ISA 1:11–1:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:23-Matt5:24\">MAT 5:23–5:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21-Amos5:24\">AMO 5:21–5:24</a></p>",
